version_description:
This version includes the following improvements and fixes :

• fixed an issue where playback was not resumed automatically when app runs in the background or device is locked;
• fixed crash that might occur when switching favorite stations;
• fixed crash that might occur when you insert links from the clipboard by adding custom stations;
• added save for recent search results;
• other minor changes and improvements.

Improvements and bug fixes for iOS8:
- improved performance;
- fixed bug in wake up and sleep timers;
- fixed bug in player when app in background.

Introducing a brand new "Radio".

We have completely updated all, so now it has become much easier, clearer and faster.

"Radio PLUS" * - for real music lovers, who are aware of the new songs, add them to wishlist and buy on iTunes.
And also use the equalizer to enhance the sound.

Other changes:
- Improved search by genres, categories, styles;
- Now you can find information about the current song or station on the Internet, copy the link to the radio to easily share with your friends;
- For the current playing song added option to search videos on YouTube ™;
- Improved songs recognition algorithms;
- Energy consumption is reduced up to 3 times;
- Added the equalizer with a lot of presets;
- Added "Auto" mode for the equalizer, which automatically adjusts for every song and station;
- Fixed minor bugs and flaws.

* "Radio PLUS" is also available for free use for a limited time.

- added fade-on and fade-out effects for sleep timer and wakeup alarm;
- improvements;
- bugfix;

Introducing "Radio" for OSX, download from the Mac App Store.

Changes in this update:
- added widget "Radio": now you can start one of the three latest used stations;
- Added a new option "Open Player": selecting station will open player window;
- Added a new option "Save traffic": in background mode app will not download additional data and album art;
- Added a new option "Start Playing": when you start the app will playing the last used station. It is very convenient to use it with Siri: "Siri, turn on the radio!";
- A lot of small improvements.

