Hello everyone, we are finally back!
All the old and annoying bugs are fixed:
- fixed the problem with uploading images for manually added stations;
- fixed errors in the alarm clock;
- adapted the application for iOS12 and the newest iPhone X;
- fixed the error with changing the order of stations in the "My stations" section;
- updated the widget of quick access to "My stations" (on the screen of widgets and notifications of iOS and when you press 3D Touch on the application icon).

Added features about which you asked us:
- button "Apple Music", which opens the track you selected in the "Music" app;
- a new app for Apple Watch with the ability to use the wheel to adjust the volume (waiting for your feedback and suggestions for further improvements).

More than 1000 stations were updated, and they also brought another moderator to our team, which will help us quickly track and update the stations that changed broadcasting, as well as add new ones!

